Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你是结城梨斗的未婚妻对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那对我来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 一直以来谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后由我选择自己该走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:23.08,title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fad(450,450)\blur4\ pos(529.467,390.767)}守护的东西和被守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了 村雨前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你我才能取回身体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样又能吓前辈玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  娜娜和梦梦为什么都穿着我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 因为情况紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺能干的嘛 芽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和村雨静合作 把我割离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的身体是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实体化了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然涅墨西斯和小暗和芽亚小姐不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股黑色气场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似曾相识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦梦 老姐在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涅墨西斯 虽然有很多事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静小姐 我们去救姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你把事情传达给提亚悠老师和御门老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要去吗 芽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦 得让小暗姐姐变回原样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你阻止我也要去哦 小涅墨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小涅墨 听着不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗 快变回原来的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是结城梨斗的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏起来也是毫不犹豫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是真的梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太…太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈同学 小暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 得快点追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 去更衣室把「The dial」带上比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可结城君他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心哦 不知羞耻的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗姐姐只是在做怪梦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得叫醒她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万能工具要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我不同以往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 佩凯 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内裤里侧和传送门连在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩凯 快把内裤这部分暂时解除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为现在的我可是不知羞耻的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩凯 衣服要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所构建的纳米纤维被侵蚀了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 小暗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呻吟声不错啊 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑滑的 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬邦邦喷雾君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰冻滑滑君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美柑 连四年级的都向你表白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过我拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是美柑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷倒学弟的魔力女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 美柑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没去迷别人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我清楚了 菈菈公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你就是我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了结城梨斗 和他的灵魂合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我这恋爱之路的绊脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈大人 危险 这能量太巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:07:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗把能量用完的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定就能变回原样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨斗 能暂时保持这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和梨斗在一起 我一定能发挥出超常的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说恋爱就必须杀掉对方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈大人 被压制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马隆？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没关系 梨斗和这座城市由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我消失吧 你这碍眼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒过来 小暗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然抵消了我的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈 没事…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 你…你的身体变小了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量好像用过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消耗过多能量超过极限值 身体就会变小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是戴比鲁克星人特有的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈大人你太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说菈菈的父亲也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他变得更小了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前戴比鲁克星王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在银河大战最后关头横扫战场之后就变小了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过消耗过头就变小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴比鲁克星真是狂人辈出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗 你还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这幅模样 下一发就抵消不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她的能量也耗尽了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 没有变回原来的小暗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能量了？别说笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过稍微多用了点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就能再次充填了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不拘泥于大范围攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变身能力也不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩凯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使不上劲儿 这下麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦啦 真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的全用光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这回真的要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等小暗 你的目标是我才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金色暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了个碍事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马鲁 普瓦茨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉来晚了 菈菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到光柱我们就赶过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到竟然变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎斯汀 今天不是短篇的截稿日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在那都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫画家只不过是临时身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是考虑到菈菈大人和妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持一定距离生活而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直都是戴比鲁克皇家亲卫队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿这衣服一点说服力都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对大叔用色色的招数也只会恶心人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真烦 真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明显很不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金色暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要伤害菈菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可不能视而不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 扎斯汀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准打架哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜 梦梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小不点是老姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨斗前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 不愧是前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一上来就这样啊 你这禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这么精神我就放心了 梨斗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦梦 娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们跑哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来话长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请自行想象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎斯汀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是金色暗影的妹妹 芽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 你也是我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜大人 梦梦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候就别胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚是我们的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 小暗也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来不是为了和小暗小姐战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是为了让她恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菈菈前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了菈菈前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了牵制住了小暗姐姐 不惜变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这城市和梨斗前辈没事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗姐姐就还能变回原样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚 有什么方法让她变回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神潜入行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 小暗姐姐只是发动了被植入的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是被什么给寄生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是有希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 小暗姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池骚乱是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是涅墨西斯所策划的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐也变回原样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要杀死梨斗前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要杀死梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 芽亚也是来碍事的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他交给姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我可要对你做不该做的事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜 梦梦 这里就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚是想要打倒小暗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是策略
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让小暗恢复原状的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要反抗姐姐吗 芽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所认识的真正的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候一定会说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「结城梨斗是我的目标」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「不会让别人杀死的」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涅墨西斯说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Darkness说不定有bug
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Darkness如此看重好色之事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对梨斗前辈也是非一般的执着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无疑问是受到了梨斗前辈影响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Darkness程序本该让内心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全染上兵器破坏的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗姐姐心中对梨斗前辈的记忆却未受影响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗姐姐的心还没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变身Darkness有残缺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是bug的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 小暗的心还残存着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我和娜娜送到芽亚的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是因为小暗在意芽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而无意识做出的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚的作战策略正基于此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的光好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢 也不像打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们不知道的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害的人正为了世界而战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美 你漫画看多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上世界的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能这么做的还真有那么几个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要我这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的能让小暗变回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都只不过是推测
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用精神潜入或许能确认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚的内心可能因此被Darkness侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只有赌一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就看小暗的内心和梨斗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得这策略有点蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 芽亚比我们更了解内心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她确信有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽亚一直全力战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消耗着暗影的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能尽量减少梨斗的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也愿意相信芽亚所说的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕有一丁点儿让小暗变回来的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜 梦梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴在身上就能换装的换装程序备用品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面装了你们的正装数据哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好保护梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 梨斗一定能回应大家的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下 娜娜大人 梦梦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让你们做这么危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人就拜托扎斯汀你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过五分钟它们就会回去电脑猎场了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽力的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变身的精度完全没有下降
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和菈菈前辈的对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该已经耗去破坏两三次星球的能量了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 无限能量不可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的战斗肯定有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表情不错 芽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就更想让你受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是老让结城梨斗舔你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这对他来说太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是不知羞耻的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他无法靠自己的意识张牙舞爪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让姐姐替他满足你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的 根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在精神潜入的时候 我被真正的梨斗前辈舔过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那时的兴奋感相比
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？ 那就看你能坚持多久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在高潮的瞬间杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能坚持几秒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆之树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨…梨斗前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 结城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特意上门送死的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了对你做尽色事才过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就让你见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我准备好
